              <span id="reviewTextContainer618924547" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12756412095155589688">I would have liked it better if it wasn&apos;t so depressing. I like happy endings. Story is strong, but whow is the guy crazy in the book. I hope I never meet someone like that.</span>
  <span id="freeText12756412095155589688" style="display:none">I would have liked it better if it wasn't so depressing. I like happy endings. Story is strong, but whow is the guy crazy in the book. I hope I never meet someone like that.</span>
